{"tid":1325762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣布 所有政府工都係奶共","createTime":"2019-07-17T03:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T08:04:26.000Z","uid":277811,"like":6,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c03af0221dece8caebba76f6580d762679dbdb65","tid":1325762,"uid":277811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>我知我好偏激！<br />\n我知連登好多人都係入境撚 但所有政府工都係奶呀爺奶共 無一倖免 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以 唔好叫啲狗轉咩入境消防懲教救護 成班一擔擔逗政府份狗糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好以為自己係清泉醒未 所有政府工都係狗啊屌你！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"></span>鐘意請比個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f02156a80ca27cf53289363ba44c15ca87b0d3","tid":1325762,"uid":136640,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:46:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">P牌 分化 負皮完唔洗覆</span></span>"},{"pid":"c9d8d3a8cba51a4e6a891a449b497919661c5d42","tid":1325762,"uid":71988,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">已有好多奶共份子偷偷留下負皮<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>奶共政府狗罪名如下:<br />\n狗:收呀爺錢打9香港人<br />\n入境:日日幫呀爺放150件大陸人來港鳩鳴生仔<br />\n消防:幫新腥港人救火救人,濫救無辜<br />\n救護:日日協助新腥港人來港醫院生仔 剝削香港醫療資源<br />\n懲教:協助大陸犯罪份子改過自新 搞亂香港 <br />\n海關:協助新腥港人走私水貨<br />\n你地唔好諗住洗白!你地唔好忘記你地有份奶共!<br />\n一定要齊心屌爆佢地老母!!!!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"123e3c17dcfcda252247502ef08be3ff5e28ca3d","tid":1325762,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:05:20.000Z","msg":"（7.21）香港人？拍馬都追唔上法國啦！（中聯辦/銅鑼灣？）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1325745\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1325745</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"73cf1ce5f4dac9f2fdbff7e3a9d4c6bdca133bba","tid":1325762,"uid":277811,"like":1,"dislike":0