daa8fd4dea20c11e28c","tid":1325762,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:38:15.000Z","msg":"on9論點論證"},{"pid":"8ec87765a2bf17cf153188b85725c6e1ee90ac42","tid":1325762,"uid":277811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf61e957d8b97c2bfee6614f49107f021a61e129","tid":1325762,"uid":36612,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:30:07.000Z","msg":"淨係覺得做入境都係幫兇<br />\n個DEPT 推行咁多賣港政策 係入面做都係幫兇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:24:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我真係火燒心口！</span><br />\n睇到叫人做境 單程證每日配額150個 <br />\n日日發生既事 香港公屋就係留哂比佢地 <br />\n又用番個句 打份工姐 入境幫兇狗 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇到想屌好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">sor9ry我知會屌親好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"98a6c33abf0121660d09113d8574ec8e74774057","tid":1325762,"uid":127121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:02:49.000Z","msg":"黃絲做政府工好過藍絲做<br />\n唔通比深藍，黨員，入去做政府工好咩<br />\n班友又貪污又私相授受<br />\n就係缺少左各位義士，有良心之士做政府工<br />\n政府先咁腐敗，又劣政，又惡法，又送錢比大陸<br />\n各路好漢立場同意志堅定就唔會被污染(不過現實好多受染左，所以更加需要有良知既人加入)<br />\n自己做政府工，就係要守住個底線，唔做仆街野，唔欺負平民百姓<br />\n返到公司擺明同深藍同事嘈<br />\n每次遊行都有去<br />\n我心不死，撤回惡法<br />\n721見！"},{"pid":"9909109f416e6bfbb8bae32567c77e4f7f667aad","tid":1325762,"uid":246980,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c03af0221dece8caebba76f6580d762679dbdb65","tid":1325762,"uid":277811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>我知我好偏激！<br />\n我知連登好多人都係入境撚 但所有政府工都係奶呀爺奶共 無一倖免 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以 唔好叫啲狗轉咩入境消防懲教救護 成班一擔擔逗政府份狗糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好以為自己係清泉醒未 所有政府工都係狗啊屌你！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"></span>鐘意請比個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:04:26.000Z","msg":"邊撚個係你阿爺？"}]}